ate things. A possible solution might be to separate JUnit tests to assert precomputed values, but that could limit coverage. I should check the output XML for dynamic report details.", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_0034f1349302b464016a3e6a46c21c819798046b4742d1e64e\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"content\":[],\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABqPmp7pLkD1JVLz2id7C1gIklWO9DFA2rmw633bH1WF1TV0iCZu37pho5y59ryOjSasYOLgBXxW4TjFu3VWRtO69V7hde0TfCkhHs8SEQXTQWDSfmiDQO2rad62jefG2CvOIrUZ2gnW4rINu4ITOdkYdpTVfHjmTenso2yp2yKJXShcCt1AnrMreICOHbNWzKvU3TlQXF63C6Zqq0k2GoFrPE_-OtZVBs27kxq2xqxHb6IGr3dEuYmmx20uZXDKt-F6zJHYNlPsvlE8d5HTDLePw8M3gKZPLhVehruRMNkyD27qIfqSIEnE-zEXgE3I0DDWM3xBIXSGjk21d1FQHSo7_TZ0pZJuTdxPyoc0EqJijIElWn6MeE1Tv58k3rcV6e4egAdnUp-KRrKhVI3uiRlkH5RZKx4pwFyHOPskDczTb85RHfjDbFOS3hv5B98H74svF6GjibXw58JR9BfP4TH7wxrRvj8jwXn_iE2_Inn1o8TVrTBOcMHNe5JT6JHzenq79teSSEq0to2Zy2xcvtsVYqWyuxtuFscLoLMtUS1zyrryxMA7uQ74l532yCkwH2VNv_pPYWLmwUDiZV6YIHy_8zwZdVnpo-WVM4u1hf7nyTaZp-ZjrkdQyBP8DC-UNZSUgSESikAJyeQcYfRQeOn3WmEZH0APg_OFarwVJSkdeiADPeSCfECnBFyFITfJGmoJm07CRnINg5oDUt1jPY4PHSWQFX85OTAGf4mUJkHUnU7qZ_hO9FTl_rK_2dvVQUr0cSgZKUXA4yLEeMVmc6XTEXMTXBNWrjK8-Bh2AUskDvvrJyzXkoVP4CDHp1ACvzMbknu1RSq06psCKO7rzstc5DEcqoj6fxZ7Ft6tybh115_VFHJGclCak4WI4W_Gitbq4hYuyzeV9W8lzrVipWKxWv4RR_knCHXQqL6XvSwDLKY__hnIyDWwGVjmBXSgAnjq4YkT8gA8UwZHVS1kjtp12E4ZMVs5hZLfh7XlhYiL9hQcyz4MiRh6O2rso52ZbgXFbdmNWqMtGoX2LCsXY-cZJpO4JM01LKViBqubHaGN7BlNhDL7Wi1Fz8gurtMKLnVc5UptkfqSGNwj4lNsw-TFlZKKh0t9rJ8uAogkrAFO7iP5BbhTPrCdesFbY33nfIzYx1hM0cZIl0JVlnSgUSyWxwjzhtx5eMPTGsD5nSThPfp1NkVjYljShIPDzGpop7nw10BvCH2kHax11-RaIoSrVEEsZ5lfqy2wlULjXFwFQX2cXLq-zQUQUMNrBfVOgRbh9_PtCFXSFsEl4gGhn5jrVfK8vyp8M2g1GJA1kC5Y8Yp3btz-Aypn-nXtknOCk1a1GNCU1bUf4yRn6PwqNwgWSfYFitU6NoJ5VtJnhcOnVdc4vvyxQ08WlzfYZ6tamKt1fT8KZCh7mghB-Xxufj6SajpNZboXokm5CmqxmwL9wro4pIb_ZytpLeDw3EPxzMXxk9utQkKIlI_Qc3EA6PubbZjWxTdn9vtM1Z_lTJJ1i3nTYac4djJCVOLkduphcA0sO1Wop_MxBaS2jzT5jRfky-L09BUjODSmgTc-cC2y6RMtzX5CwbroX8zwYMb_G-Js3LYAlYce4GSoP-fdKKLFI_nlLTsQW0u7LfoEza-O8vYoa4uWYnNW6uM