eratum-macros_3/1.9.0/build.gradle`\n- Adds `-Yretain-trees`, required for supported `ValueEnumMacros.find*ValueEntriesImpl` use.\n\nConclusion: the remaining dynamic-access sites in `enumeratum.ValueEnumMacros$ValueOfFromExpr.unapply` should be left uncovered rather than covered via unsupported internal or Native-Image-unsafe mechanisms.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0034f1349302b464016a3e6aab60bc8197a5595979e785a4cb\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 23899, "output": 2333, "cacheRead": 49664, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 75896, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782475394076, "responseId": "resp_0034f1349302b464016a3e6a82b30c8197b946473ab3b31160"}, "toolResults": []}
